## 16. Naming Conventions

The project uses explicit prefixes to avoid ambiguity.

| Prefix | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `mapbiomas_` | Indicator derived from MapBiomas data |
| `inpe_` | Indicator derived from INPE / TerraBrasilis / PRODES |
| `environmental_` | Project-derived environmental screening output |
| `chunk_` | Document chunking output |
| `clean_` | Text cleaning output |

Examples:

```text
mapbiomas_native_vegetation_area_ha
inpe_prodes_deforestation_area_ha
environmental_risk_score
chunk_text
clean_text
```

