## 18. Data Quality Notes

Before using the panel, check:

- missing municipality codes;
- inconsistent year values;
- duplicated municipality-year records;
- negative area values;
- unexpected zero values;
- mismatched municipality codes between MapBiomas and INPE;
- abrupt changes that may indicate source or preprocessing issues.

---

## 19. Interpretation Principle

The structured indicators should be interpreted as:

```text
environmental evidence for screening
```

They should not be interpreted as:

```text
legal proof
```

The final principle is:

> The data dictionary defines analytical variables used for evidence organization and screening. 
  It does not define legal responsibility, environmental guilt or regulatory non-compliance.
